      <title rev="FAC 2020-03 December 13, 2019" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">4.2105</ph> 
         <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-017?>Solicitation
provisions and contract clause.<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 4.2105 by—
a.  Revising the section heading;
?></title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li id="id1989H0Z10BA" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d326e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The contracting officer shall
insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                        base="id1989I600I4C"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>,
Representation Regarding Certain Telecommunications and Video Surveillance
Services or Equipment–</p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d326e33" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> In all solicitations for contracts;
and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d326e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Under indefinite
delivery contracts, in all notices of intent to place an order,
or solicitations for an order (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                           <ph rev="FAC 2020-03 December 13, 2019" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-017?>e.g.<?FM MARKER [Why] b.  Removing from paragraph (a)(2) “i.e.” and adding “e.g.” in its place; and?></ph>
                        </i>, subpart <xref href="FAR-i1117301.dita#i1117301"
                              base="i1117301"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8.4</xref> and <xref href="FAR-i1104008.dita#i1104008"
                              base="i1104008"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d326e67" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-52.204-25.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                        base="id1989I600I4C"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-25</xref>, Prohibition
on Contracting for Certain Telecommunications and Video Surveillance
Services or Equipment, in all solicitations and contracts.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d326e79" class="- topic/p ">
