shall insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-26.dita#id19CAC0P0ESS"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">52.204-26</xref>, Covered Telecommunications
Equipment or Services-Representation, in all solicitations.<?FM MARKER [Why] c.  Adding paragraph (c).?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
